释义：
come forward 站出来，拿回信息、想法等
字面含义为站(come)出来(forward)，表示为了发言或传递东西而“向前站”。
例句：
Why don't you just come forward and tell the police about that?
你怎么不站出来告诉警察？
The boys came forward one by one and gave Kate gifts.
男生们一个个站出来给凯特礼物。
Thank you for coming forward with this.
谢谢你能指出问题。
对话：
A: How did the police find the criminal?
警察们是怎么找到罪犯的？
B: Someone came forward with information about him.
有人站出来举报了他。